Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.80,0:23:47.70,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惡意的矛頭
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.65,0:01:15.45,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0250,,#17 Throne強襲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-------------------------------------------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.91,0:00:28.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 記憶卡之類的全都被取出了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.52,0:00:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來這裏早已廢棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.56,0:00:32.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是花了6年才來到這兒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.70,0:00:34.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豈能空手而歸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.11,0:00:42.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根據資料  這前面應該是居住區
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.67,0:00:47.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.48,0:00:48.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.08,0:00:51.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.94,0:00:54.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寵物機器？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.68,0:00:57.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 這個是情報終端
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.72,0:01:01.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿迪 找到寶了 先歸航
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.76,0:01:03.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩準備解析數據
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.84,0:01:05.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.20,0:01:12.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和第一第二代機體都不同
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.00,0:01:15.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Veda的數據裏 不存在的Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.00,0:01:18.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真有這樣的機體嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.43,0:01:21.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管有無 我們都親眼看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.03,0:01:22.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.60,0:01:25.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實看到了 確實看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.51,0:01:36.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,類似Gundam的MS 至少有三架
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.01,0:01:46.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然和我們的太陽爐不同 但也能釋放類似GN粒子的物體
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.06,0:02:03.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 你們是被那些Gundam所救咯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.56,0:02:04.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.77,0:02:23.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.93,0:02:26.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些機師通過通信說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.90,0:02:29.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己是Gundam Meister
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.60,0:02:34.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 走時還把這個宙域點的數據傳給了我們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.46,0:02:36.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們的目的是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.91,0:02:38.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是來打招呼的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.67,0:02:40.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喏 我們可是前輩嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.08,0:02:43.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會是陷阱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.83,0:02:46.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙救了剎那他們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.85,0:02:48.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話雖如此
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.66,0:02:50.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見個面就知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.62,0:02:54.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去迎接新的Gundam Meister吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.43,0:02:57.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光學攝影機捕捉到接近中的物體
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.70,0:02:58.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顯示在主屏幕上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.03,0:03:00.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.95,0:03:07.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲爾德 做好Exia的出擊準備
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.91,0:03:10.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,克莉絲負責掃瞄那架艦艇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.09,0:03:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.50,0:03:14.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被偷窺了 被偷窺了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.06,0:03:17.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事嗎 沒事嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.29,0:03:20.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來是在防備我們吧 隨他們的便
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.92,0:03:23.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.24,0:03:24.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.37,0:03:31.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會錯 接近中的艦艇釋放的確實是GN粒子
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.81,0:03:32.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.04,0:03:35.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艦內確認有4台GN drive
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.62,0:03:36.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然如此
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.78,0:03:39.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 他們是怎麼搞到太陽爐的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.71,0:03:42.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 艙門打開了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.83,0:03:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米迦勒 妮娜 抓穩咯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.69,0:03:57.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.45,0:04:02.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我們看到的機體
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.84,0:04:04.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.91,0:04:07.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確認從MS發來的光通信
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.79,0:04:10.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請求許可在托勒密著艦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.92,0:04:12.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回復說允許著艦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.61,0:04:15.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 解除Exia的待機
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.43,0:04:17.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓剎那去戰術指令室
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.13,0:04:18.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.71,0:04:20.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.76,0:04:23.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獲得著艦許可 前往普特萊瑪奧斯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.33,0:04:50.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝批准我們著艦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.89,0:04:57.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是Throne Eins的Gundam Meister 約翰·崔尼蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.13,0:05:02.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是Throne Zwei的Gundam Meister 米迦勒·崔尼蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.09,0:05:06.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是Throne Drei的Gundam Meister 妮娜·崔尼蒂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.01,0:05:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們都好年輕
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.40,0:05:11.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且名字…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.51,0:05:15.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們有血緣關係 是親兄妹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.58,0:05:18.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 誰是Exia的機師？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.80,0:05:19.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.86,0:05:21.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.18,0:05:22.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.00,0:05:29.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我Exia的Gundam Meister 剎那·F·清英
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.11,0:05:30.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.18,0:05:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡擅自行動的Meister
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.63,0:05:38.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這點非常對我胃口
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.40,0:05:45.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別碰我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.77,0:05:48.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小子 竟敢這麼對我妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.18,0:05:50.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你妹妹冒犯在先吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.85,0:05:53.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴 你這個薄情的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.38,0:05:55.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想被劃兩刀嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.56,0:05:57.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 米迦勒
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.42,0:05:59.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹掉他 幹掉他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.24,0:06:02.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 哥哥 哥哥 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.44,0:06:04.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然是哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.83,0:06:06.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想你 好想你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.81,0:06:07.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.03,0:06:10.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你誰啊 你誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.11,0:06:11.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈羅 哈羅
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.61,0:06:13.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去死吧 去死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.16,0:06:20.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 記憶沒了…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.55,0:06:26.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 站著說話也不方便 去房間裏說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.20,0:06:27.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.53,0:06:45.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們 就是新的Gundam Meister
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.81,0:06:48.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們第一次意見相同呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.70,0:06:49.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你指什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.01,0:06:52.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不說也明白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.91,0:06:57.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些人真誇張
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.58,0:06:59.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭那女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.20,0:07:02.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 難道不成你對剎那…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.48,0:07:04.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這意思
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.45,0:07:09.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種Gundam 爸爸媽媽沒對我說過
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.70,0:07:14.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們為什麼會擁有Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.05,0:07:18.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼Veda的數據庫裏沒有那種機體
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.52,0:07:22.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無可奉告 我們有保秘的義務
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.03,0:07:24.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.14,0:07:29.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太陽爐…不 你們從哪獲得GN Drive的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.29,0:07:31.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 不能回答
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.71,0:07:33.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.65,0:07:36.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你們是來幹什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.57,0:07:43.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特來拜見一下被舊型號MS整慘的差勁Meister啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.16,0:07:44.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.37,0:07:47.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說笑呢 說笑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.47,0:07:50.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人不爽 我失陪了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.91,0:07:52.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後麻煩向Veda提交報告書
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.82,0:07:54.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.60,0:08:02.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可惜 要是女人的話我就不會置之不理了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.38,0:08:03.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米迦勒
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.44,0:08:04.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.26,0:08:09.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約翰哥 我覺得好無聊 我去船裏各處探險了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.72,0:08:10.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.75,0:08:12.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.46,0:08:17.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.65,0:08:19.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.79,0:08:27.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可別惹我生氣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.01,0:08:39.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 能告訴我們一點嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.05,0:08:43.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們使用那些Gundam想做些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.62,0:08:46.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是根除戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.45,0:08:47.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.05,0:08:53.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你們一樣 我們也是Gundam Meister
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.49,0:08:55.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說 是要和我們聯手嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.89,0:08:58.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白癡 誰要跟你們聯手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.31,0:09:03.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不是你們的介入太軟弱 哪會輪到我們出場啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.55,0:09:05.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.32,0:09:08.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,字面意思 你們太不可靠了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.03,0:09:11.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 不完整的改造人同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.96,0:09:13.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.61,0:09:14.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 要打嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.92,0:09:19.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在對不起 我為弟弟的無禮道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.70,0:09:29.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 給我們下命令的人 應該是對你們的武力介入報有疑問吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.47,0:09:32.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們是棄子？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.34,0:09:35.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請繼續保持以往的作戰行動
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.79,0:09:40.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們將以自己的判斷來進行武力介入
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.69,0:09:46.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在伊奧利亞·舒恩伯格的計劃中是必要的存在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.54,0:09:54.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道呢 這在我們今後的行動中應該能得以實現
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.27,0:09:59.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰把Gundam交給那種傢伙的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.79,0:10:03.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 要讓Veda對情報進行驗證
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.32,0:10:08.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Veda的終端 竟然開著？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.90,0:10:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰在那裏
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.59,0:10:22.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 你怎麼進來的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.32,0:10:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣進來的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.97,0:10:35.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你… 你們到底是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.86,0:10:38.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.73,0:10:44.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這麼走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.26,0:10:46.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說完想說的就回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.76,0:10:50.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那個叫約翰的傢伙還不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.12,0:10:52.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.59,0:10:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 什麼時候拍的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.58,0:10:57.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.89,0:11:00.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣讓他們回去了好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.23,0:11:03.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對方的情報完全沒有摸清
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.36,0:11:04.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也未必
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.00,0:11:05.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.84,0:11:07.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.07,0:11:08.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你們談話的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.70,0:11:11.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是去調查了那台叫Throne的機體哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.26,0:11:14.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵呵 不愧是戰術預報師
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.16,0:11:18.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報告書請上傳到獨立終端
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.86,0:11:21.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不要輸入Veda
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.88,0:11:24.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.51,0:11:29.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.64,0:11:35.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜 那個Exia的機師是叫剎那來著？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.79,0:11:37.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種傢伙有什麼好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.59,0:11:40.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是很可愛嗎 妮娜一見鍾情了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.93,0:11:44.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 下次見面看我不把他打下來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.52,0:11:47.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任務來了 任務來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.13,0:11:50.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來 真會使喚人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.76,0:11:56.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有必要讓世界見識一下 「天人」的真正實力
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.02,0:12:02.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你的珍貴情報 利馮茲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.08,0:12:05.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝神讓我遇到了你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.44,0:12:09.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不正是為此才收留我的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.29,0:12:12.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 那次相遇是命運的安排
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.63,0:12:17.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括我成為「天人」的監視者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.92,0:12:19.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想對世界做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.91,0:12:21.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼也不會做
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.65,0:12:28.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是個監視者 僅僅為觀察世界的變革而存在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.91,0:12:32.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於結束了 定期測驗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.49,0:12:35.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快死了 還要兼顧打工什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.00,0:12:38.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在考前請個假不就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.67,0:12:40.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易絲你還真好意思說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.08,0:12:41.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.82,0:12:42.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.87,0:12:44.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼 怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.59,0:12:47.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 到哪兒去散心？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.21,0:12:49.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有想看的電影…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.90,0:12:53.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我得回西班牙一趟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.30,0:12:55.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,參加表哥的婚禮
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.40,0:13:00.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 那就好好放鬆下吧 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.06,0:13:02.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別出軌哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.84,0:13:03.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.93,0:13:05.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別出軌哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.43,0:13:07.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.38,0:13:13.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前輩 累了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.59,0:13:16.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,取材一直沒收穫
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.24,0:13:19.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說了嗎  各陣營的官方回應
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.85,0:13:26.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嚴重損毀的MS共計87架 陣亡人數超過200
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.49,0:13:32.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 據戰地士兵稱 出現了新的Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.86,0:13:35.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的Gundam？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.71,0:13:41.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未經過證實 不過看來「天人」也有秘密武器
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.77,0:13:44.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道那位士兵的所屬和姓名嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.45,0:13:48.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是從池田先生那裏聽說的 可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.08,0:13:50.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上聯繫他 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.47,0:13:52.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.06,0:13:57.24,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,{\fs20\an2}UNION軍 太平洋上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.69,0:14:01.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不僅任務失敗 還損失了三名優秀的Flag Fighter
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.74,0:14:04.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真是不配做隊長啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.39,0:14:05.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是沒有辦法的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.94,0:14:10.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新型Gundam突然出現 完全出乎意料
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.35,0:14:12.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說到底是性能天差地別
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.08,0:14:16.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少要有和Gundam同等性能的機體
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.12,0:14:18.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Flag是我軍的最新銳機體
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.78,0:14:20.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道 可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.92,0:14:25.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,達利爾 我們是Flag Fighter 拿出點骨氣來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.35,0:14:29.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.82,0:14:33.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 有突入大氣層的機體？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.16,0:14:35.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Gundam嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.16,0:14:37.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 預測降落地點是？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.29,0:14:40.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什… 什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.08,0:14:43.65,Notes,NTP,0000,0000,0050,,{\fs20\an2}UNION 美國 MSWAD基地
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.97,0:14:45.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我的假說沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.94,0:14:50.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam的能源供應系統是利用了拓撲缺陷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.65,0:14:53.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的話 所有事都能對上號了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.12,0:14:55.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam機體數量稀少的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.37,0:14:59.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及為什麼需要200多年時間
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.22,0:15:05.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種能源供應系統 只能在木星製造
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.54,0:15:10.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,120年前的載人木星探查計劃…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.96,0:15:14.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那項計劃莫非和Gundam的開發有關
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.93,0:15:16.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果真是這樣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.15,0:15:21.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊奧利亞·舒恩伯格的真正目的 並非根絕戰爭
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.73,0:15:24.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.60,0:15:30.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「你知道的太多了…」
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.74,0:15:32.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.22,0:15:34.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.27,0:15:35.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觀測室通告
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.91,0:15:41.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三架疑似Gundam的MS 從EW9877方向接近基地
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.71,0:15:42.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全MS部隊出動…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.89,0:15:44.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.92,0:15:48.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向各基地請求增援
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.02,0:15:51.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未知機體 可用肉眼捕捉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.06,0:15:52.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太快了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.71,0:15:58.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些Gundam 是新型的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.61,0:16:00.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到達目標地點
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.52,0:16:03.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮娜 合體 一口氣殲滅
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.88,0:16:04.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.54,0:16:17.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高濃度GN粒子傳輸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.99,0:16:25.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說 目標是我？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.18,0:16:27.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GN粒子輸送完成
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.77,0:16:32.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白 Throne Eins GN Launcher(高能炮)發射
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.30,0:17:16.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀呼 厲害  不愧是大哥 做事真露骨
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.48,0:17:22.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了 來了 雜魚一大群
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.77,0:17:25.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長 三架新型機
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.01,0:17:27.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一看就知道
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.22,0:17:30.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的基地…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.08,0:17:32.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,格拉漢姆
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.88,0:17:33.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,片桐！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.40,0:17:38.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教授他… 艾佛曼教授他…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.57,0:17:40.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.97,0:17:46.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忍無可忍無須再忍 絕不饒你 Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.20,0:17:47.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.39,0:17:52.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼啊 讓我也消遣消遣吧 大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.34,0:17:55.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別怕 馬上就結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.64,0:17:59.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破壞 蹂躪  最後殲滅
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.24,0:18:00.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上吧 Fang
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.42,0:18:05.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這又怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.69,0:18:09.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.82,0:18:18.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈瓦德
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.57,0:18:24.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看招吧 Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.91,0:18:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.83,0:18:33.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是Flag的實力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.05,0:18:38.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去會死 才怪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.56,0:18:43.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈瓦德
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.51,0:18:45.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈瓦德·梅森
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.23,0:18:57.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長 Flag是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.76,0:19:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是Fang
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.06,0:19:10.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,解氣了吧 撤退
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.25,0:19:11.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.88,0:19:13.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下面還有任務
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.01,0:19:16.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam Meister都是大忙人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.76,0:19:18.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.69,0:19:20.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隊長
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.57,0:19:23.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別盲目追擊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.78,0:19:30.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,教授… 哈瓦德…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.88,0:19:37.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底想羞辱我幾次 Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.46,0:19:41.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙襲擊了美軍基地？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.95,0:19:42.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目的呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.99,0:19:46.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明 Veda也沒有收到情報
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.97,0:19:48.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自作主張
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.66,0:19:53.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們今後還怎麼混
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.98,0:20:01.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Meister嗎 那些傢伙 真的是Gundam Meister嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.27,0:20:08.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心 路易絲 代我向伯父伯母問好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.14,0:20:09.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.74,0:20:11.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先不管這些
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.46,0:20:14.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.72,0:20:16.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離別的吻呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.35,0:20:18.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吻我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.49,0:20:22.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.15,0:20:24.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈 太認真了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.67,0:20:27.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 我喜歡這樣的沙慈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.97,0:20:29.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路易絲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.87,0:20:31.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我走了 恩
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.45,0:20:54.69,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}同じ笑顔してた　そんな僕らも　幾年も重ね過ぎて
